| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-1487 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhouse)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 7eac919e-75da-5c70-96b4-f032bbcae69b"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
